response.original_title: スペースチャンネル 5 ウキウキ ミュージック フェスティバル オンライン
response.overview: The 20th anniversary event of the "Space Channel 5" series, "Space Channel 5" Uki Uki Music Festival," was scheduled to be held on March 23, 2020, but had to be postponed to prevent the spread of the COVID-19. Since the situation is still unpredictable, we decided to hold the event as "Space Channel 5" Uki Uki Music Festival Online", with the same performers and contents as originally planned, but with no audience. Here is a digest video of the event.
response.title: SPACE CHANNEL 5 UKIUKI MUSIC FESTIVAL ONLINE
